OL,3,CMan given life sentence for fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FA man from Bristol has been given a
OL,7,Flife sentence after fatally stabbing
OL,8,Fsomeone else during an altercation.
OL,10,FJegir Asaad stabbed 39-year-old Tomasz
OL,11,FStankiewicz with a knife in Filton
OL,12,FAvenue, Horfield, in the early hours
OL,13,Fof Wednesday 21 August.
OL,15,FDashcam footage, captured by a passing
OL,16,Ftaxi, showed Asaad with a knife that
OL,17,Fwas later linked to the murder by
OL,18,Fdetectives.
