OL,3,CMan given life sentence for fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,FThe 24-year-old was convicted of
OL,7,Fmurder following a two-week trial at
OL,8,FBristol Crown Court.
OL,10,FHe will serve a minimum of 23 years in
OL,11,Fprison as part of his life sentence
OL,12,Fbefore he can be considered for parole.
OL,14,F'My grandchildren have lost their
OL,15,Fdaddy' - victim's family
OL,17,FIn a statement read in court, the
OL,18,Fmother of Mr Stankiewicz said her
OL,19,Fson's death had caused "horrible pain"
OL,20,Fand left a "void" in her life.
