OL,3,CMan given life sentence for fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,F"We would like to express the horrible
OL,7,Fpain and void that we have had in our
OL,8,Fhearts since the moment my son Tomasz
OL,9,Fwas so brutally taken away from us in
OL,10,Fthe most inhumane way," she said.
OL,12,F"For us, every minute of this case is
OL,13,Fa reminder that the life of our family
OL,14,Fhas been changed forever.
OL,16,F"We are left with the feeling of void
OL,17,Fand incomprehensible shock and pain.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@WO]
