OL,3,CMan given life sentence for fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,F"Tomasz has been taken away from us,
OL,7,Fsomeone who was not only a son, a
OL,8,Fbrother, but also a father to two
OL,9,Flittle girls.
OL,11,F"My grandchildren have lost their
OL,12,Fdaddy ` and there won't be a single
OL,13,Fday in their lives when they will not
OL,14,Fhave to cope with the fact that they
OL,15,Fwill never see him again. They will
OL,16,Fnever again be able to spend time
OL,17,Ftogether.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
