OL,3,CMan given life sentence for fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing
OL,6,F"As a mother, I have lost a part of
OL,7,Fme. My heart has been torn to little
OL,8,Fpieces and there are simply no words
OL,9,Fthat could describe how much I miss my
OL,10,Fonly son.
OL,12,F"How much I would like to hear his
OL,13,Fvoice saying: 'I love you, mum', how
OL,14,Fmuch I long to be able to feel him
OL,15,Fnext to me again.
OL,17,F"It does not matter how old my son was
OL,18,Fwhen his life was taken away from him.
OL,19,FFor a mother a child always remains
OL,20,Fher child, regardless of their age."
